-size:12pt;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Cabin; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.9871999999999999;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Máte další otázky?</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.656;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.9871999999999999;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Cabin;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Přečtěte si také <a href="https://pttglobal.nulisec.com/page/frequently-asked-questions" target="_blank">Časté Dotazy</a>. Pokud budete potřebovat další informace, kontaktujte nás prosím na adrese lukas@nulisec.com</span></p>